[
  {
    "start": 7.12,
    "end": 13.2,
    "text": "Hello my friends and welcome back to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 9.84,
    "end": 16.0,
    "text": "Easy Speak English podcast. My name is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 13.2,
    "end": 18.56,
    "text": "John and I'm really happy that you're",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 16.0,
    "end": 21.279,
    "text": "here with me today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 18.56,
    "end": 24.8,
    "text": "In this episode, we are going to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 21.279,
    "end": 30.4,
    "text": "practice English together for just five",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 24.8,
    "end": 33.76,
    "text": "minutes. Yes, only five minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 30.4,
    "end": 36.96,
    "text": "It's short, it's simple, and it's",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 33.76,
    "end": 40.879,
    "text": "perfect for busy people. You don't need",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 36.96,
    "end": 42.48,
    "text": "a a notebook. You don't need a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 40.879,
    "end": 46.559,
    "text": "classroom.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 42.48,
    "end": 49.2,
    "text": "And you definitely don't need hours of",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 46.559,
    "end": 52.239,
    "text": "free time.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 49.2,
    "end": 56.32,
    "text": "You just need five minutes and your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 52.239,
    "end": 60.64,
    "text": "voice. This is what I like to call snack",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 56.32,
    "end": 63.12,
    "text": "learning. Small pieces of practice",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 60.64,
    "end": 66.64,
    "text": "but very powerful",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 63.12,
    "end": 68.799,
    "text": "like healthy snacks for your English",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 66.64,
    "end": 73.2,
    "text": "brain.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 68.799,
    "end": 76.4,
    "text": "You can do this practice anytime. You",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 73.2,
    "end": 80.799,
    "text": "can do it in the morning while making",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 76.4,
    "end": 84.24,
    "text": "coffee. You can do it while walking. You",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 80.799,
    "end": 89.119,
    "text": "can even do it quietly before you sleep.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 84.24,
    "end": 94.159,
    "text": "It's easy to fit into your daily life.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 89.119,
    "end": 98.799,
    "text": "So here is your job for today. It's very",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 94.159,
    "end": 103.2,
    "text": "simple. Listen to my voice. Repeat after",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 98.799,
    "end": 106.64,
    "text": "me and speak with me.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 103.2,
    "end": 108.799,
    "text": "Don't worry about mistakes. Don't worry",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 106.64,
    "end": 112.64,
    "text": "about pronunciation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 108.799,
    "end": 114.56,
    "text": "Just listen. Speak and flow with the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 112.64,
    "end": 117.52,
    "text": "language.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 114.56,
    "end": 120.799,
    "text": "If you enjoy this kind of short",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 117.52,
    "end": 124.719,
    "text": "practice, please tell us in the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 120.799,
    "end": 128.08,
    "text": "comments. If many people like it, we",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 124.719,
    "end": 130.16,
    "text": "will definitely make more episodes like",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 128.08,
    "end": 133.12,
    "text": "this.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 130.16,
    "end": 136.319,
    "text": "Now, let's talk about today's topic.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 133.12,
    "end": 141.599,
    "text": "It's one of my favorite topics. It's",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 136.319,
    "end": 145.599,
    "text": "called the power of small habits.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 141.599,
    "end": 149.84,
    "text": "Many people believe that success comes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 145.599,
    "end": 154.72,
    "text": "from big actions. They think they must",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 149.84,
    "end": 158.72,
    "text": "study for hours every day. They think",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 154.72,
    "end": 162.4,
    "text": "they must read many books in one month.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 158.72,
    "end": 168.4,
    "text": "They think they must change everything",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 162.4,
    "end": 172.959,
    "text": "at the same time. But the truth is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 168.4,
    "end": 176.48,
    "text": "that's not how real change happens. Real",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 172.959,
    "end": 181.28,
    "text": "change does not happen in one big",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 176.48,
    "end": 185.76,
    "text": "moment. It happens in many small moments",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 181.28,
    "end": 189.2,
    "text": "repeated every day. Think about brushing",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 185.76,
    "end": 193.28,
    "text": "your teeth. You don't brush your teeth",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 189.2,
    "end": 196.959,
    "text": "for two hours once a month.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 193.28,
    "end": 199.68,
    "text": "You brush for two minutes every day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 196.959,
    "end": 203.519,
    "text": "That small habit keeps your teeth",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 199.68,
    "end": 207.28,
    "text": "healthy. Learning English works in the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 203.519,
    "end": 210.64,
    "text": "same way. It's not about one big weekend",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 207.28,
    "end": 213.12,
    "text": "of study. It's about small daily",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 210.64,
    "end": 216.319,
    "text": "actions.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 213.12,
    "end": 220.799,
    "text": "Five minutes of listening,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 216.319,
    "end": 222.799,
    "text": "five minutes of speaking, five minutes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 220.799,
    "end": 226.879,
    "text": "of shadowing.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 222.799,
    "end": 229.599,
    "text": "These moments may feel small now, but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 226.879,
    "end": 233.44,
    "text": "over time",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 229.599,
    "end": 237.92,
    "text": "they create big results and there is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 233.44,
    "end": 242.08,
    "text": "science behind this. When you repeat a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 237.92,
    "end": 246.959,
    "text": "small action every day, your brain",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 242.08,
    "end": 249.439,
    "text": "changes. Your brain creates a new path,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 246.959,
    "end": 254.0,
    "text": "a new road.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 249.439,
    "end": 260.4,
    "text": "The first time you do it, the road is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 254.0,
    "end": 264.08,
    "text": "weak and slow. But every time you repeat",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 260.4,
    "end": 267.759,
    "text": "it, that road becomes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 264.08,
    "end": 271.36,
    "text": "stronger and faster.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 267.759,
    "end": 275.6,
    "text": "At first, speaking English feels",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 271.36,
    "end": 280.0,
    "text": "difficult. You stop, you think, you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 275.6,
    "end": 283.36,
    "text": "search for words. That's normal.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 280.0,
    "end": 288.639,
    "text": "That's part of learning.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 283.36,
    "end": 292.639,
    "text": "But with small daily practice,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 288.639,
    "end": 295.68,
    "text": "something beautiful happens. Your words",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 292.639,
    "end": 299.36,
    "text": "come faster. Your tongue moves more",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 295.68,
    "end": 302.96,
    "text": "easily and speaking becomes more",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 299.36,
    "end": 308.16,
    "text": "automatic. Automatic means your mouth",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 302.96,
    "end": 312.56,
    "text": "speaks without your brain panicking.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 308.16,
    "end": 315.759,
    "text": "Small habits are powerful because they",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 312.56,
    "end": 317.44,
    "text": "are easy. They don't need strong",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 315.759,
    "end": 320.88,
    "text": "motivation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 317.44,
    "end": 324.96,
    "text": "You don't need to feel excited. You just",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 320.88,
    "end": 330.96,
    "text": "do them. And that's when real learning",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 324.96,
    "end": 333.199,
    "text": "begins, not in big events, but in small",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 330.96,
    "end": 337.919,
    "text": "daily actions.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 333.199,
    "end": 342.24,
    "text": "Here is a very important secret. If you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 337.919,
    "end": 344.479,
    "text": "want to build a habit, start small, very",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 342.24,
    "end": 348.639,
    "text": "small.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 344.479,
    "end": 353.6,
    "text": "If you plan to study one hour every day,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 348.639,
    "end": 357.759,
    "text": "you might quit. After one week, but if",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 353.6,
    "end": 361.039,
    "text": "you plan just five minutes, you will",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 357.759,
    "end": 364.96,
    "text": "probably do it. It's almost impossible",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 361.039,
    "end": 367.759,
    "text": "to fail 5 minutes, right?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 364.96,
    "end": 371.52,
    "text": "You can shadow English while making",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 367.759,
    "end": 374.639,
    "text": "coffee. You can repeat sentences while",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 371.52,
    "end": 379.36,
    "text": "brushing your hair. You can whisper",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 374.639,
    "end": 384.08,
    "text": "English sentences while walking.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 379.36,
    "end": 388.56,
    "text": "Small moments are easy to repeat",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 384.08,
    "end": 393.44,
    "text": "and repeatable moments grow.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 388.56,
    "end": 395.039,
    "text": "5 minutes becomes 10 minutes. 10 minutes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 393.44,
    "end": 399.52,
    "text": "becomes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 395.039,
    "end": 403.12,
    "text": "20 minutes. And soon",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 399.52,
    "end": 407.039,
    "text": "English becomes a natural part of your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 403.12,
    "end": 410.96,
    "text": "life. Let me tell you a short real",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 407.039,
    "end": 415.6,
    "text": "story. I once had a student who was very",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 410.96,
    "end": 420.08,
    "text": "shy. He was afraid to speak English.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 415.6,
    "end": 423.84,
    "text": "Even simple sentences scared him.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 420.08,
    "end": 427.599,
    "text": "So we started with one small habit.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 423.84,
    "end": 430.8,
    "text": "Every morning he spoke to himself for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 427.599,
    "end": 434.24,
    "text": "just two minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 430.8,
    "end": 436.8,
    "text": "At first he said very simple things. I'm",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 434.24,
    "end": 439.12,
    "text": "getting ready. I'm making coffee. I'm",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 436.8,
    "end": 443.759,
    "text": "going to work.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 439.12,
    "end": 448.88,
    "text": "After a few weeks, his sentences became",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 443.759,
    "end": 450.88,
    "text": "longer. After two months, he could tell",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 448.88,
    "end": 455.199,
    "text": "short stories.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 450.88,
    "end": 457.919,
    "text": "And after six months, he joined a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 455.199,
    "end": 461.36,
    "text": "speaking club.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 457.919,
    "end": 465.039,
    "text": "2 minutes changed everything. It",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 461.36,
    "end": 469.52,
    "text": "transformed his confidence. So, here is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 465.039,
    "end": 471.599,
    "text": "my message for you today. Don't chase",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 469.52,
    "end": 476.0,
    "text": "big goals.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 471.599,
    "end": 480.08,
    "text": "Build small habits.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 476.0,
    "end": 484.08,
    "text": "Small habits improve your English. Small",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 480.08,
    "end": 488.879,
    "text": "habits build your confidence. And small",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 484.08,
    "end": 493.84,
    "text": "habits slowly change you. This fiveinut",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 488.879,
    "end": 497.759,
    "text": "podcast can be one of those habits.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 493.84,
    "end": 501.52,
    "text": "Listen every day. Repeat often. and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 497.759,
    "end": 506.72,
    "text": "trust the process. You may not feel",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 501.52,
    "end": 511.599,
    "text": "progress in one day, but in a few weeks,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 506.72,
    "end": 514.8,
    "text": "you will be surprised by yourself.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 511.599,
    "end": 518.959,
    "text": "Thank you so much for practicing English",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 514.8,
    "end": 523.2,
    "text": "with me today. This is John from Easy",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 518.959,
    "end": 527.2,
    "text": "Speak English Podcast. Keep shadowing,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 523.2,
    "end": 532.399,
    "text": "keep learning, and keep believing in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 527.2,
    "end": 538.6,
    "text": "yourself. Bye for now. And don't forget",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 532.399,
    "end": 538.6,
    "text": "tomorrow at 700 p.m. be with us.",
    "textdich": ""
  }
]